high_descs: Turn left and take one step, then turn right and walk to the counter.
Take the lettuce that is on the counter.
Turn around and take two steps, then turn left and walk across the room.
Open the fridge and put the lettuce inside, then close the fridge door for three seconds, then open the fridge and take the lettuce out.
Turn to the left and take one step, then turn right and face the counter.
Put the lettuce on the counter to the left of the salt shaker.
Go ahead to counter between sink and microwave.
Pick up lettuce from back of counter.
Open fridge, put lettuce on top shelf.  Close refrigerator door.  Wait four seconds.  Open refrigerator door.  Remove lettuce and close door.
Turn left, proceed until reach counter next to refrigerator.  Turn right to face counter.
Place lettuce on counter, in front of toaster and to the left of salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: Move lettuce to refrigerator, cool, move it to counter.

high_descs: Turn left, hang a right at the counter and walk to the counter with the dishwasher ahead.
Pick up the head of lettuce to the right of the microwave on the counter.
Turn around, hang a left at the counter and walk to the white fridge ahead.
Put the head of lettuce inside the fridge on the top shelf off to the right side, chill it for seven seconds, remove it and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the counter on the right next to the fridge.
Put the chilled head of lettuce in between the green soap bottle and the salt shaker on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled head of lettuce on a counter.
